        " عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «مَنْ تَزَوَّجَ اِمْرَأَةً فِي إِحْرَامِهِ فُرِّقَ بَيْنَهُمَا وَ لَمْ تَحِلَّ لَهُ أَبَداً »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2711 - Imam (as) said: \"Whoever marries a woman while in the state of ihram, they shall be separated, and she will never be permissible for him.\""
        ]
      }
